; Coverage test for post.cc resolve_expr with result.is_long
; When an amount expression evaluates to a long integer (not an amount),
; resolve_expr converts it via result.to_amount().
; Using (2 * 5) yields a long; using ($5 * 2) would yield an amount.

2024/01/01 Test Long Expr
    Expenses:Food    (2 * 5)
    Assets:Cash

test reg
24-Jan-01 Test Long Expr        Expenses:Food                    10           10
                                Assets:Cash                     -10            0
end test
